ces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26be2cd004fd9ce49b717760f0ca03fadda567cb","tid":1496754,"uid":54303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f76b89ccaf662eaf48342f5db4ccdc358d9e9247","tid":1496754,"uid":42740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:06:28.000Z","msg":"推 好撚恐怖 搞晒誇國公司"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"所以絕對唔可以縱容中國橫行霸道"},{"pid":"90d7bf8e652edeb7bdbc721d10fe0b89dffb6723","tid":1496754,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"而家即刻同我係電話SET每晩十點<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1496636</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnzZ2rL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnzZ2rL.png&h=79e33ac3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n大叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問記性唔好今日十點半先記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都set鬧鐘就唔會唔記得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順手提提身邊朋友！"},{"pid":"7c28866cd109b4d993ff69b4b77a5759366ed7cb","tid":1496754,"uid":6435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"呢單野唔信陳雲都唔得"},{"pid":"f07baef8cc5782d443d93af0996077615111e723","tid":1496754,"uid":171866,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"三、解決方法：從受政治威懾的航空界員工而言，可以投訴國際航空運輸協會（IATA）等國際組織，及要求國際航空工會之類的組織介入，並且一定要向美國的貿易談判代表團（負責人是Robert Lighthizer）正式提交投訴，舉報中國干預香港的國際航班協定及干預在香港的外國私人企業的內部運作。如果中國這次干預得逞，香港及國際在香港的私人企業將遭受同一模式的打擊，這正正就是美國貿易代表團最懼怕的事。一旦美國貿易代表團將是次國泰員工事件納入貿易談判關注的項目，員工的就業就安全了。<br />\n我認為香港的私人企業，應該借助是次時間，將香港受中國政治干預企業的情況告知美國的貿易談判代表（必要時可以要求美方守秘密），使到香港的企業自主性得到足夠的保護。<br />\n中國又一次準確地犯錯。香港人如果識得把握機會，可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將香港的個案送交美國貿易代表Robert Lighthizer處理</span></span>。<br />\n這種國際關係知識和策略，香港恐怕只有陳雲懂得和夠膽提出。即使當作是國際視野，各位也應該廣傳此帖文給朋友閱讀，裝備自己。"},{"pid":"f123127db35eb14c4076246dc8a0ba9b898c8a98","tid":1496754,"uid":54303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"中國人萬一富強左，白色恐怖就必定蔓延到全球<br />\n佢地成日都吹噓自己係全球最大市場，唔可以比佢地坐大，唔可以比佢地用經濟影響全球政治！"},{"pid":"a69dfc2c8d97b79e7e3cf526896d887f5d8e14a7","tid":1496754,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c28866cd109b4d993ff69b4b77a5759366ed7cb","tid":1496754,"uid":6435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"呢單野唔信陳雲都唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"係，同埋呢排佢出少左果類膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62f29754cf7d9941fb247f88b00e5d9b16a4f60","tid":1496754,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906cde33e506100313f1ac9b51de6947ad1fe09e","tid":1496754,"uid":280593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db9c62bd9bfb43c16ba83a5e906a70482d8a0b9b","tid":1496754,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"陳雲：國泰航空公司員工的危機，有更妥當的國際解決辦法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好因人廢言，睇睇陳雲呢篇文先（食左藥）<br />\n大家唔想自己生計受打擊，就用twitter等方法搵番美國相關人士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"trump 同pench 